<!-- ====== Blog Details Start ====== -->
<section class="ud-blog-details">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">

			<div class="col-lg-8">
				<div class="ud-blog-details-content">
					<h2 class="ud-blog-details-title">
						@Model.Name
					</h2>
					<p class="ud-blog-details-para">
						@Model.Description
					</p>
					<h3 class="ud-blog-details-subtitle">Virtual Private Server</h3>
					<p class="ud-blog-details-para">
						Our server solutions are custom designed to deliver optimal performance
						and ultimate scalability as your business grows. Powered by Intel’s next
						generation architecture, you can be assured of maximal availability for
						your production environment.
					</p>
					<div class="ud-blog-quote">
						<i class="lni lni-quotation"></i>
						<p>
							Lead management lowered our postage costs by more than thirty percent and our service revenue grew to more than twenty thousand.
						</p>
						<h6>“Amazon Elite Home Improvement”</h6>
					</div>
					<h3 class="ud-blog-details-subtitle">Dedicated Firewall</h3>
					<p class="ud-blog-details-para">
						To protect services exposed to a public IP address, we offer a
						hardware-based Firewall that is configured and integrated into
						our Anti-DDoS infrastructure. It limits exposure to distributed
						denial of service attacks by dropping specified network flows
						coming from outside our network.
					</p>
					<h3 class="ud-blog-details-subtitle">Client Certificate Authentication</h3>
					<p class="ud-blog-details-para">
						With mutual (two-way) SSL Authentication, the client presents a certificate
						to the server which is then mapped to a user identity known to both the operating s
						ystem and the application itself. In this way, system administrators have ultimate
						control over server resources, regardless of the level of access granted by the
						application. Using simple file system permissions and database access control
						policies, business rules can be enforced without in depth knowledge of the
						application itself.
					</p>
					<h3 class="ud-blog-details-subtitle">Document Management</h3>
					<p class="ud-blog-details-para">
						Imagine having at your fingertips every document you’ve ever created, neatly organized 
						and accessible from anywhere you happen to be. Anything you can scan and upload to the 
						server and photos can be captured on the spot, no upload necessary, just click the Camera 
						icon and shoot.
					</p>
					<h3 class="ud-blog-details-subtitle">Desktop Backup</h3>
					<p class="ud-blog-details-para">
						With our exclusive automation system, not only will you have backups that exist
						on your server but downloaded to your laptop as well. In plain English terms, this
						means your data is never locked away and inaccessible.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-4">
				<div class="ud-blog-sidebar">
					<div class="ud-newsletter-box">
						<img src="~/assets/images/blog/dotted-shape.svg"
							 alt="shape"
							 class="shape shape-1" />
						<img src="~/assets/images/blog/dotted-shape.svg"
							 alt="shape"
							 class="shape shape-2" />
						<h3 class="ud-newsletter-title">What are you waiting for?</h3>
						<p>Improve efficiency today!</p>
						<form class="ud-newsletter-form">
							<button asp-controller="Cart" asp-action="Add" asp-route-id="@Model.ProductId" class="ud-main-btn">@Model.TargetName</button>
							<p class="ud-newsletter-note">Secured with 1024 bit encryption</p>
						</form>
					</div>

					<div class="ud-articles-box">
						<h3 class="ud-articles-box-title">Popular Articles</h3>
						<ul class="ud-articles-list">
							<li>
								<div class="ud-article-image">
									<img src="~/assets/images/blog/article-author-01.png"
										 alt="author" />
								</div>
								<div class="ud-article-content">
									<h5 class="ud-article-title">
										<a href="javascript:void(0)">
											The 8 best landing page builders, reviewed
										</a>
									</h5>
									<p class="ud-article-author">Martin Fedous</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li>
								<div class="ud-article-image">
									<img src="~/assets/images/blog/article-author-02.png"
										 alt="author" />
								</div>
								<div class="ud-article-content">
									<h5 class="ud-article-title">
										<a href="javascript:void(0)">
											Create engaging online courses your student…
										</a>
									</h5>
									<p class="ud-article-author">Glomiya Lucy</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li>
								<div class="ud-article-image">
									<img src="~/assets/images/blog/article-author-03.png"
										 alt="author" />
								</div>
								<div class="ud-article-content">
									<h5 class="ud-article-title">
										<a href="javascript:void(0)">
											The ultimate formula for launching online course
										</a>
									</h5>
									<p class="ud-article-author">Andrio jeson</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li>
								<div class="ud-article-image">
									<img src="~/assets/images/blog/article-author-04.png"
										 alt="author" />
								</div>
								<div class="ud-article-content">
									<h5 class="ud-article-title">
										<a href="javascript:void(0)">
											50 Best web design tips & tricks that will help you
										</a>
									</h5>
									<p class="ud-article-author">Samoyel Dayno</p>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
